
This directory contains assorted stock quote scripts.

value_portfolio is a stand-alone perl script for updating and printing
    the value of a portfolio.  To use this script, edit the the first 
    few lines at the top of the file to indicate your portfolio and 
    purchase price.
    (from Christopher B. Browne, cbbrowne@hex.net)

getquotes.pl is a set of perl routines to fetch stock quotes from various
   services.  dervied from the above. Still under development.
 

Finance::YahooQuote
    This is a perl 5 module that will pull one or more stock quotes from
    Yahoo! Finance.  From  version 0.06 by Dj Padzensky <djpadz@padz.net>.
    Home site at http://www.padz.net/~djpadz/
